{
  "id": "69c72e64f6cf6984d3e1d196",
  "title": "infobox日記",
  "created": 1774661228,
  "updated": 1780772973,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c72e64f6cf6984d3e1d196",
      "text": "infobox日記",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661228,
      "updated": 1774661228
    },
    {
      "id": "69c72e6c0000000000903ac4",
      "text": "infoboxで日記をつける",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661228,
      "updated": 1774661244
    },
    {
      "id": "69c72e6c0000000000903ac5",
      "text": "`YYYY-MM-DD`のページを作って、[infobox]を置く",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661229,
      "updated": 1776245271
    },
    {
      "id": "69c730bf000000000014dd2a",
      "text": "`YYYY-MM-DD`のページに[アイコンリンク]用の画像を用意する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661823,
      "updated": 1777762144
    },
    {
      "id": "69c731b6000000000014dd2f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774662070,
      "updated": 1774662070
    },
    {
      "id": "69c72f5e0000000000903aca",
      "text": "infoboxに登録するには、`#YYYY-MM-DD`のページにリンクをつなげる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661470,
      "updated": 1774662117
    },
    {
      "id": "69c72fab0000000000903acb",
      "text": "#YYYY-MM-DD （infoboxに登録される）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661547,
      "updated": 1774662137
    },
    {
      "id": "69c72fac0000000000903acc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661549,
      "updated": 1774661549
    },
    {
      "id": "69c730e5000000000014dd2b",
      "text": "infobox以外の用途でリンクを使いたい場合は、アイコンリンクを使う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661862,
      "updated": 1776245293
    },
    {
      "id": "69c73159000000000014dd2e",
      "text": "このリンクはinfoboxから拾われない→[YYYY-MM-DD.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661977,
      "updated": 1774662041
    },
    {
      "id": "69c73140000000000014dd2d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661952,
      "updated": 1774661952
    },
    {
      "id": "69c73493000000000014dd31",
      "text": "[日付形式のアイコンリンク]によって、[関連ページ]を増やさないで昨日、明日といった日付のリンクができる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774662804,
      "updated": 1777763436
    },
    {
      "id": "69c73493000000000014dd32",
      "text": "例: [2026-03-11.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774662804,
      "updated": 1774663030
    },
    {
      "id": "69c73493000000000014dd33",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774662804,
      "updated": 1774662804
    },
    {
      "id": "69df5ebe0000000000d531e5",
      "text": "[** infobox日記とは]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776246463,
      "updated": 1776246486
    },
    {
      "id": "69df5aa90000000000d531e1",
      "text": "　[井戸端日記]（[共同日記]）とは別の[共同日記]です",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776245418,
      "updated": 1776246708
    },
    {
      "id": "69df5adf0000000000d531e4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776245472,
      "updated": 1776245472
    },
    {
      "id": "69df5eda0000000000d531e6",
      "text": "[** infobox日記の特徴]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776246490,
      "updated": 1776246550
    },
    {
      "id": "69df5ef70000000000d531e7",
      "text": "　[infobox]（[文芸的データベース]）の機能を使った分散型アーキテクチャ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776246520,
      "updated": 1776246704
    },
    {
      "id": "69df5f190000000000d531e8",
      "text": "　日付ページ（`YYYY-MM-DD`のページ）に日記の一覧と概要が表示されるので、読みたい日記だけ読むことができる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776246553,
      "updated": 1776247097
    },
    {
      "id": "69df651d0000000000d531ef",
      "text": "　code:mermaid",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248094,
      "updated": 1776248188
    },
    {
      "id": "69df65730000000000d531f0",
      "text": "  graph LR",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248179,
      "updated": 1776248194
    },
    {
      "id": "69df65730000000000d531f1",
      "text": "  M[日付ページ（YYYY-MM-DD）]---A[Aさんの日記（#YYYY-MM-DD）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248179,
      "updated": 1776248294
    },
    {
      "id": "69df65f80000000000d531f2",
      "text": "  M---B[Bさんの日記（#YYYY-MM-DD）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248312,
      "updated": 1776248331
    },
    {
      "id": "69df66300000000000d531f3",
      "text": "  M---C[Cさんの日記（#YYYY-MM-DD）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248368,
      "updated": 1776248381
    },
    {
      "id": "69df613a0000000000d531ea",
      "text": "　[- 他人に遠慮せずに日記ページを編集することができる]（できないみたい）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776247098,
      "updated": 1777762209
    },
    {
      "id": "69df67eb0000000000d53200",
      "text": "　 ページを小さく維持することができる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248812,
      "updated": 1776248843
    },
    {
      "id": "69df680b0000000000d53201",
      "text": "　 必要とあれば長文も載せることができる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248843,
      "updated": 1776248891
    },
    {
      "id": "69df61980000000000d531eb",
      "text": "　[トピック指向]と相性が良い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776247192,
      "updated": 1776334705
    },
    {
      "id": "69df61cd0000000000d531ec",
      "text": "　　トピック別に複数の[日記ページ]を作成することができます",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776247245,
      "updated": 1777763475
    },
    {
      "id": "69df66700000000000d531f4",
      "text": "　　code:mermaid",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248433,
      "updated": 1776248447
    },
    {
      "id": "69df667f0000000000d531f5",
      "text": "    graph LR",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248447,
      "updated": 1776248447
    },
    {
      "id": "69df667f0000000000d531f6",
      "text": "    M[日付ページ（YYYY-MM-DD）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248447,
      "updated": 1776248463
    },
    {
      "id": "69df66860000000000d531f9",
      "text": "    M---A1[Aさんの仕事日記（#YYYY-MM-DD）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248454,
      "updated": 1776248527
    },
    {
      "id": "69df667f0000000000d531f7",
      "text": "    M---A2[Aさんのグルメ日記（#YYYY-MM-DD）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248447,
      "updated": 1776248536
    },
    {
      "id": "69df667f0000000000d531f8",
      "text": "  トピック別に分割できるので、ひとつのページが重くなる確率は低くなります",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248447,
      "updated": 1776250092
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1aa390000000000e589c4",
      "text": "  [トピック指向日記]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776396858,
      "updated": 1776396875
    },
    {
      "id": "69df5f190000000000d531e9",
      "text": "　ひとつの日記ページに複数の日付をいれることができる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776246554,
      "updated": 1776247387
    },
    {
      "id": "69df625b0000000000d531ee",
      "text": "　　`#YYYY-MM-DD`　は[ハッシュタグ]なので、ちがう日付のハッシュタグを複数設置することができます",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776247387,
      "updated": 1777763500
    },
    {
      "id": "69df62250000000000d531ed",
      "text": "　　code:mermaid",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776247334,
      "updated": 1776248604
    },
    {
      "id": "69df671b0000000000d531fb",
      "text": "    graph LR",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248604,
      "updated": 1776248604
    },
    {
      "id": "69df671b0000000000d531fc",
      "text": "    M1[日付ページ（YYYY-MM-01）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248604,
      "updated": 1776248621
    },
    {
      "id": "69df673a0000000000d531ff",
      "text": "    M2[日付ページ（YYYY-MM-02）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248634,
      "updated": 1776248653
    },
    {
      "id": "69df671b0000000000d531fd",
      "text": "    M1---A[Aさんの日記（#YYYY-MM-01 , #YYYY-MM-02）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248604,
      "updated": 1776248701
    },
    {
      "id": "69df671b0000000000d531fe",
      "text": "    M2---A",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248604,
      "updated": 1776248712
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67c3400000000007a9991",
      "text": "[** infobox日記の役割]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777761333,
      "updated": 1777761353
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67c7b00000000007a9994",
      "text": " 実験、テストとしての側面",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777761404,
      "updated": 1777761406
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67c7f00000000007a9995",
      "text": "  Cosenseのinfobox（文芸的データベース）機能の実験",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777761408,
      "updated": 1777761465
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67cb900000000007a9996",
      "text": "　Cosenseのページ作成の練習としての側面",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777761466,
      "updated": 1777761554
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67d1600000000007a9997",
      "text": "　 [ページ作成への抵抗感]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777761559,
      "updated": 1777761824
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67d2500000000007a9998",
      "text": "　 [ページ作成の意図]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777761574,
      "updated": 1777761819
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67d3000000000007a9999",
      "text": "　 [初手新規ページ作成]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777761584,
      "updated": 1777761795
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67e5800000000007a999a",
      "text": " 個人的な記録としての側面",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777761881,
      "updated": 1777761890
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67edd00000000007a99a0",
      "text": "  [文章を書く練習]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777762013,
      "updated": 1780772973
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67eef00000000007a99a1",
      "text": "  [下書き]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777762032,
      "updated": 1777762067
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67e5a00000000007a999b",
      "text": "  [出来事の記録]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777761883,
      "updated": 1777761909
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67e5a00000000007a999c",
      "text": "  [行動ログ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777761883,
      "updated": 1777761906
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67e5a00000000007a999d",
      "text": " 　[備忘録]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777761883,
      "updated": 1777761964
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67e5a00000000007a999e",
      "text": " 　[内省]・[自己理解]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777761883,
      "updated": 1777761978
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67e5a00000000007a999f",
      "text": " 　[自己啓発]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777761883,
      "updated": 1777761988
    },
    {
      "id": "69f685c4000000000018ecb2",
      "text": " コミュニケーションの場としての側面",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777763781,
      "updated": 1777763785
    },
    {
      "id": "69f685ee000000000018ecb3",
      "text": " 　[意見交換]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777763823,
      "updated": 1777763839
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67c3400000000007a9992",
      "text": " [日記ページの役割]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777761333,
      "updated": 1777761881
    },
    {
      "id": "69f67c3700000000007a9993",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777761335,
      "updated": 1777761335
    },
    {
      "id": "69df671a0000000000d531fa",
      "text": "[** infobox日記の書き方]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248602,
      "updated": 1777761333
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6800200000000001ece36",
      "text": "　1. ページを作ってinfobox日記を書く",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777762307,
      "updated": 1777762389
    },
    {
      "id": "69e0c31f0000000000094110",
      "text": " 　まず、日記の[ページタイトル]を考えます",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776337695,
      "updated": 1777762350
    },
    {
      "id": "69e0c3610000000000094112",
      "text": " 　ページを作ります",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776337761,
      "updated": 1777762350
    },
    {
      "id": "69e0c38a0000000000094113",
      "text": " 　ページの中に記事を書きます",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776337802,
      "updated": 1777762350
    },
    {
      "id": "69e0c3b70000000000094114",
      "text": " 　ハッシュタグ `#YYYY-MM-DD`をつけてinfobox日記に登録します",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776337847,
      "updated": 1777762350
    },
    {
      "id": "69ebfc6c0000000000a5dd2c",
      "text": "　2. 既にあるページをinfobox日記にする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777073261,
      "updated": 1777762517
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6803400000000001ece37",
      "text": " 　ハッシュタグ `#YYYY-MM-DD`をつけてinfobox日記に登録します",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777762357,
      "updated": 1777762526
    },
    {
      "id": "69f680ea00000000001ece39",
      "text": " 　　ページタイトルは適切か",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777762538,
      "updated": 1777762569
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6811f00000000001ece3a",
      "text": " 　　ベージの内容に足りない部分はないか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777762591,
      "updated": 1777762620
    },
    {
      "id": "69f680dd00000000001ece38",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777762526,
      "updated": 1777762526
    },
    {
      "id": "69f681d200000000001ece3b",
      "text": "[** infobox日記の外し方]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777762771,
      "updated": 1777762782
    },
    {
      "id": "69f681d500000000001ece3c",
      "text": "　ハッシュタグ `#YYYY-MM-DD`を削除すれば、infobox日記に登録から外れます",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777762774,
      "updated": 1777762839
    },
    {
      "id": "69f681ec00000000001ece3d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777762797,
      "updated": 1777762797
    },
    {
      "id": "69e0c3300000000000094111",
      "text": "[日付タグ] - [日付ページ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776337713,
      "updated": 1777762797
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5fb5c000000000011ee79",
      "text": "[エバーグリーンノート]（[Evergreen notes]）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777728348,
      "updated": 1777728422
    },
    {
      "id": "69ebfc5a0000000000a5dd2a",
      "text": "[トピック指向文芸的データベース]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777073243,
      "updated": 1777755441
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6652c000000000033a643",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777755437,
      "updated": 1777755437
    },
    {
      "id": "69c72e920000000000903ac6",
      "text": "[https://img.shields.io/badge/🌱-infobox日記-white#.png]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661267,
      "updated": 1777728648
    },
    {
